1. Write function to find sum of odd numbers from 1 to n.
Import java.util.*; 
public class Functions{
   ...>     public static void sumofOdd(int n){
   ...>         int sum = 0;
   ...>         for(int i =0;i<=n;i++){
   ...>             if  (i % 2 != 0)
   ...>             sum = sum + i;
   ...>         }
   ...>         System.out.println(sum);
   ...>     }
   ...>     public static void main(String [] args){
   ...>         Scanner  sc = new Scanner(System.in);
   ...>         int n = sc.nextInt();
   ...>
   ...>         sumofOdd(n);
    }
 }
|  Output:

